Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,A... ki... ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[MILULUN]\NJeez, Aki-lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.19,Main,,0,0,0,,That was nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Milulun's so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NI have to... keep doing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:30.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NSelector battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,And what's your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith's scar,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I want it to heal...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\N...as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it will if you're lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, Aki-lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NAre you all right, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't get hurt, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just a little\Nshaken up, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,No, wait. I need to\Napologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You had to suffer\Nthrough a battle for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:36.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus, Iona had to relive\Nall those painful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve your sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Both Shiro and I were\Nmade by and from Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.25,Main,,0,0,0,,So then, in essence,\Nwe're the ones who
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,created the Selector battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's Mayu's\Nfault, not yours--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You girls have every right to\Nhate us for what we've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:03:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, you've still tried\Nto save all three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I don't condone\Nwhat Mayu's done, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I do understand\Nwhere's she coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:10.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Before now, I didn't have any\Nfriends either; I was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I know how painful that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Every single time\NI left the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw so many happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,walking and talking\Nwith their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That just made me feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I was the loneliest person\Nin the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,After hearing what Iona told\Nus about Mayu's history,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.88,Main,,0,0,0,,the loneliness that\NI felt was nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,compared to the sorts of things\Nshe's had to go through...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,So, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's it, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe what's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Her real one, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean it isn't... revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Well, it always\Nfelt kind of weird to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did Mayu make the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.86,Main,,0,0,0,,to the Selector\Nbattles the way she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl who wins has\Ntheir wish taken away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,and is sealed into a card?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a really\Nhorrible thing and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,but as far as revenge goes,\Nit doesn't make much sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Things aren't as bad when\Nwe're talking like we are now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:18.55,Main,,0,0,0,,but more than anything else,\Nbeing in a card is... lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a crushing... emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NSo maybe Mayu's real wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It isn't revenge,\Nbut wanting everyone to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,know what it feels\Nlike to be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,To feel what she's been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE]\NYuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you felt that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,So from now on, I'm going\Nto keep you close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,--even when I'm sleeping, okay?\N--[YUZUKI] I'm fine! Thanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.74,Main,,0,0,0,,but come on, this is\Nmostly just weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] With everything horrible\Nthat she's put you through,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I find it rather surprising that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,you're still looking\Nat Mayu with sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWell, that's not entirely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,But if you ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I think the reason we\Nfeel the way we do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,is 'cause of how we\Nfeel for you and Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI mean, you told us that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,you and she were created\Nby and from Mayu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the case, then\NMayu can't be all bad, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NYou really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you guys became friends\Nwith us, I bet Mayu could, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,We just have to\Nconvince her to listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.55,Main,,0,0,0,,and I think we can do that\Nby speaking from our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NYeah, but, my heart aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It must be because I\Nshouldn't feel this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I'm the Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.81,Main,,0,0,0,,But even though\Nthis feeling hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.90,Main,,0,0,0,,...it's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,All I want to do is\Nkeep embracing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:05.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Why isn't Kuro the same anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Selector battles need both--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Bright light on one side, and\Nshrouded darkness on the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,If Kuro's going to\Nbe this useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,then she leaves me\Nno other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll burn her card to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Won't we, Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NI can't believe this pampering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,A private hospital room\Nfor this measly scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the Urazoe\Nfamily for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NUm, are you okay, Urith?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a minor\Nwound, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] Say, mind\Nif I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NIona passed through many hands
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,as both a LRIG and a Selector
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,after Mayu created her\Nas the Girl of Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,But where were you before\Nyou ended up as Ruko's LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,To be honest... Well, all I\Nseem to remember is meeting Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot about Mayu and Kuro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.77,Main,,0,0,0,,and everything else that\Nhappened before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though I didn't have\Nany memory of my past...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It didn't matter because\NI had Ru in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I felt like I was born\Njust to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I know why Mayu did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,She got rid of you\Nand sent you here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,because you're vomit-inducing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] She must have\Ngotten sick of your sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,little sunny spirit, clinging\Nlike gunk to her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,She couldn't take any more,\Nso it was "so long, Shiro."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet you anything that's why
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,she put you in\NRuko's hands first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko is one horrifying girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:51.89,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, she can\Ndestroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:02.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NSo, Chiyori? What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,"Even if I know the truth\Nbehind the battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm never giving up my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hoo-yeah, onto the\Nnext big battle!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] That's you in\Na nutshell, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Such incredible evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NThere's no two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.00,Main,,0,0,0,,How else could you describe\NSelector battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Win or lose, only a\Ntragic ending awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,To suggest I jump into one\Nis real messed up and mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you, the\Nvillain of a story
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,who wants to see me suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh-heh. I gotta admit,\Nthat would be amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.10,Main,,0,0,0,,--[CHIYORI growls]\N--[ELDORA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:35.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Just kidding, but\Nremember what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish is to enter\Nthe world of the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Or did you change\Nyour mind already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:40.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NGuess that answers that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:45.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NYeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.61,Main,,0,0,0,,But if I lose one more time,\NI'll be out of the game
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.65,Main,,0,0,0,,and you won't be\Nmy LRIG anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:52.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Well, sure, but\Nthere's no use dwelling on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll jump off that bridge\Nwhen we come to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, on the subject of battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,you were a human once\Ntoo, right, Eldora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What was your wish back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:06.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, uh... I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NLiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What? I just don't\Nwanna tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Treat it like one of those\Nplot twists you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get all worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:18.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, my wish totally\Nwasn't anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I was pretty into it,\Nlike you are, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NUhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NWell, in any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess we need to speak\Nwith Tama then, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NYeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It means seeing Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NGood point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko and I can go without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I appreciate\Nthe concern, but I--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[phone rings, buzzes]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NMaybe it's Urith!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:55.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[hands clap]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NPlease battle me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NIt doesn't matter which one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.43,Main,,0,0,0,,of you guys I face either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Just battle me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:09.36,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose one more time,\Ndon't you know what'll happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Justice will prevail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You're justice. Does make\Nus the evil ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Geez, you mean\Nyou still don't get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,even after what Fumio told us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NIf they won't battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\N...how's about doing it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's start the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! My Selector\NSense detects a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWh-- Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NCool. We'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NLet's take this chick on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm the Selector!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my call to make, not\Nyours, so pipe down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh wait, you're not\Nscared of losing, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[growls] No, I'm not\Nscared of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:51.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, scar-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Chorizo's gonna mop\Nthe floor with you and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.53,Main,,0,0,0,,end your wicked schemes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:10:59.49,Main,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NWait, Chiyori, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You better get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Lousy bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[phone buzzes]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:15.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:26.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[GROUP panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NRuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't think Akira's\Ngoing to chase us, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWhat gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you two mental?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you guys\Nscrew up my battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Because--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NIf you really want to battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,then we're not gonna stop you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,but be more selective\Nabout who you fight, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:45.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Whatever. It\Ndoesn't matter who we face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause no matter who I square\Noff against, I'm gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA laughs]\NPretty bold from someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:53.84,Main,,0,0,0,,who's lost twice already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI growls]\NYeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't wait to\Nwin so I can get rid of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,your snarky, back-talking\Nbutt forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Like having you\Nas a Selector is a picnic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.01,Main,,0,0,0,,--Puh-leeze!\N--[CHIYORI] What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, you little creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:07.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NI'll do it. I'll battle Chiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.31,Main,,0,0,0,,--No!\N--[YUZUKI] Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,She's lost twice already\Nnow, so her wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you know what'll\Nhappen if you beat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all right Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this, because\NChiyori is only one loss away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Wait, don't tell\Nme you're gonna let her win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You see, right before\NI had my third loss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,and my wish got reversed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko said this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Drop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Throw me away, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,She knew what would happen\Nto my wish if I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She tried to warn me in her\Nown way and give me an out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,but I just wouldn't\Nlisten to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.89,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish was to have friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:54.32,Main,,0,0,0,,so when I lost, I was\Nhurt and isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.86,Main,,0,0,0,,But hers, it's\Nnothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NAah, just shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm the one who gives\Nthe orders, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,And once I'm the heroine\Nof the WIXOSS world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,your time of\Npunishment's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NThat'll be the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NGood grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,If Fumio didn't get through\Nto her, then I say do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] If Chiyori wins,\Nthat's another story, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,if I beat her today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,then I can prevent her\Nwish from coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's what bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What'll happen to\Nher if she loses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,and her wish gets corrupted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't worry much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Her wish is based on\Nher love of WIXOSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,So the reverse of that should\Nmake her end up hating the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,If you ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,that shouldn't make her\Ncurrent situation any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI growls]\NNow I'm really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'll never have to lay eyes\Non you ever again, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NTalk to the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HITOE] Chiyori.\N--[CHIYORI] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll battle you if that's\Nwhat you really want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,--[ELDORA] Oh?\N--[CHIYORI] Uhh... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! It's battle time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's history in the making!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Behold, the first chapter\Nin a new tale of WIXOSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,A new heroine takes the mantle\Nand forges into battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Duh, I was born ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE, CHIYORI]\NOpen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NA battlefield. One just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems that there are others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,More Selectors who hunger\Nfor battle, just like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NI know... But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NOf course, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,A little at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:33.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But soon enough the\Npain will go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.29,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I've stacked sufficient wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,so just one more will\Nmake my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll become an LRIG again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,As for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:46.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll come outside and\Ngain Iona Urazoe's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NBut why would I want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You told me how\Nmuch you like Ruko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.81,Main,,0,0,0,,and how you want to\Nbe friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That is your\Nfondest wish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.11,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's truly the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.69,Main,,0,0,0,,then you and I have\Na mutual interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,See, if we win this battle,\Nthen this body will be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That'll let you be friends\Nwith Ru, not as a LRIG,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:10.41,Main,,0,0,0,,but as a human being like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NHere we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori Moonlight\NChorizo Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the dumbest name yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Chorizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NAre you okay, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NI'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, don't worry\Nabout me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't lose this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, now, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Eldora and\NYuzuki are both strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.40,Main,,0,0,0,,They are, but this match\Nis already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:39.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Since Yuzuki is\Npart of a red deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,she can burn Chiyori's\NEner every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Meaning the odds are stacked\Npretty heavily against Chiyori,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.95,Main,,0,0,0,,They are, and Chiyori\Nprobably doesn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:55.91,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way that Eldora,\Nbeing a LRIG, isn't aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If I keep this up, I'm\Ngonna lose! Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:08.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NChiyori, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NI-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NLosing's not such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] You'll be able\Nto retire from battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.35,Main,,0,0,0,,and go back to being\Na normal girl again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora, she's--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:21.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NI knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora's doing the\Nsame thing as Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:27.24,Main,,0,0,0,,They're both trying to save\NChiyori from more battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,from more pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NC'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.70,Main,,0,0,0,,--[ELDORA] Hey, girls!\N--[YUZUKI, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NI know it's out of place
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.79,Main,,0,0,0,,to ask this during\Na battle, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I lose here today,\Ndo you think maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.25,Main,,0,0,0,,you guys can be friends\Nwith this weirdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I know she looks all loony now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.01,Main,,0,0,0,,but believe it or not,\Nback when I first met her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,she dressed super-modest,\Nand to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,--was kind of a nerd.\N--[CHIYORI] Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell 'em that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWait. Did you just talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NYep, and my name is Eldora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to\Nmeet you, Selector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Like super-adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NSsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] This is so "you"!\NThink it'll look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You trying to copy my style?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with being pals,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,but wearing matching\Nclothes is kinda dorky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,then I guess you'll just have\Nto wear something else then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NI'm on paper, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Well, I think\Nmaybe I can fix that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:29.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.93,Main,,0,0,0,,--Time to draw!\N--[ELDORA] No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] She can be a\Nreal handful at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:39.18,Main,,0,0,0,,but to be honest, I was really\Nglad she was my Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll admit she can be\Na bit of a dingbat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But still, she's a good\Nperson and a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,From the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,you were planning to lose\Nthis battle, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWait, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NNot necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I just thought the odds were\Nagainst us, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like an LRIG can\Nsway the results or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You meanie! Thanks for\Nnot bothering to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Big jerk! You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.83,Main,,0,0,0,,That was so evil of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,--Take this!\N--[ELDORA] Yep, I have to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a jerk, and that's why\Nwe shouldn't be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:10.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NI meant it when I said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I was glad you were\Nmy Selector, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You're slow-headed, naive,\Nand a total spaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You dress crazy and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,you've gotta be the\Ngoofiest gal I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,That's you, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:27.36,Main,,0,0,0,,And I want you stay just like\Nthat and never change, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NAll right then, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get this mess over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,So Chiyori, what's next? Orochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,We could go into the Ener Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Or how 'bout going all out\Nwith Arts for our next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:45.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't over yet! Just\Ncome on, stupid brain, work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Think of a way to turn\Nthe tables in this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause if I don't,\Nit's gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be separated\Nfrom Eldora forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] Eldora, we'll use Life\NCloth with Spell, plus Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NAnd we'll pair Arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:15.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Cloth Crush Flash with it\Nto cause direct damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:17.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?\NChiyori, that's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\N...going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:30.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] With Yuzuki's\Ndeck being what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:34.01,Main,,0,0,0,,the odds are against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,To be honest, if you don't pull\Na Shiira within three turns,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe's gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I could lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NUh-uh, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare make yourself\Nlose on purpose, 'kay, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.85,Main,,0,0,0,,See, I wanna become a human\Nagain one day, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,But if I'm stuck with\Nan unskilled Selector
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:54.28,Main,,0,0,0,,like Chiyori here, then\Nthat's never gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NQuit crying and keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,If you put a Burst into play,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.16,Main,,0,0,0,,you still have a\Nchance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NTurn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Orochi! Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NIt's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora! You listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:25.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I promise that I'm\Nnever gonna forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:29.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That's turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I swear to you that this isn't\Ngonna be the final chapter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:34.19,Main,,0,0,0,,And when I get finally\Nget inside WIXOSS,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the heroine\Nof the story, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:39.70,Main,,0,0,0,,And then I'll make sure you're\Nthe most minor character!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NOrochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NChiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.67,Main,,0,0,0,,We've still got one last turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NNo. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:06.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NBut Chiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Despite the trash\Ntalk, I did like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NTurn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,All that's left...\Nis the finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:28.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[foosteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,"Aki-'ovely."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:49.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NNot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,No Aki-lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,No Aki-lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who'll beat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.65,Main,,0,0,0,,the one who'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NJust... Akira Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,--[VOICES chattering]\N--[MAYU] Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NShut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:40.88,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not how it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Or else, it's completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\N"This Warmth is at its Limit."
